Path of least resistance:

At the root of the repos, do
 $ mkdir opam
 $ opam init --root=opam
 $ opam repo add coq-stable https://github.com/coq/repo-stable.git
 $ opam install -j8 coq:ssreflect coq:math-comp


This project is known to compile with:
  - coq.8.4.5
  - coq:ssreflect.1.5.0
  - coq:math-comp.1.5.0